.It Nm less Ar file
Display and navigate file content in a terminal pager.
.It Nm head Oo Fl n Oc Ar file
Print the first lines of a file.
.It Nm tail Oo Fl n Oc Ar file
Print the last lines of a file.
.El

.Sh file-utils
